snippet: One of the largest earthquakes to hit California in decades rattled its northern coast, but its depth and distance from shore reduced the impact on land.
lead_paragraph: One of the largest earthquakes to hit California in decades rattled its northern coast, but its depth and distance from shore reduced the impact on land.
